<h2>Operations</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Member/Non Member</strong></li>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <i>Login</i>: To start off you will want to login, using the navbar to get to the login page and then type in your email and password and select 'User Login' button
            <img src="~/Screenshots/Figure2.png" width="350px" height="200px"/>
        </li>
        <li>
            <i>Dashboard</i>: After successfully logging in you can navigate to your dashboard which is now available on the navbar
            <img src="~/Screenshots/Figure3.png" width="1100px" height="50px"/> 
            <ul>
                <li>
                    On your dashboard you can view what classes you are registered (Figure 3) for and if they are active or canceled
                    <img src="~/Screenshots/Figure4.png" width="600px" height="400px"/>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <i>Register for programs</i>: As a member/non member you can search for classes on the programs page and register for them. You can search by class name or filter by specifics of the class.
            Notice that you can sign up yourself or if you are part of a family you can sign up anyone else in your family using the drop down. Keep in mind that when you are registering fro a class that you aren't 
            already registered for a different class at that time. Also if there is a prerequisite that is required for the class, it is up to you to know if you have completed that 
            prerequisite. You will be prompted to pay for the class when you arrive for it at the facility. Notice that when you are registering for a class the information displayed 
            shows the name, time, date, and capacity of the class. 
            <img src="~/Screenshots/Figure5.png" width="700px" height="400px"/>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    If you would like to check that you are successfully registered for a program, you can navigate back to your dashboard to see it under your currently registered classes 
                </li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <i>Become a member</i>: If you are not currently a member, you can navigate to the membership page by clicking 'Membership' in the navbar then clicking 'Sign Up'. This will take you to a screen where you
            can fill out the information and become a member!
            <img src="~/Screenshots/Figure7.png" width="700px" height="300px"/> <img src="~/Screenshots/Figure8.png" width="700px" height="200px"/>
        </li>
    </ul>
